Title: An Act Changing the Name of Talagutong Elementary School in the Municipality of Don Marcelino, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Don Marcelino Maruya Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 758
An Act Changing the Name of Talagutong Elementary School in the Municipality of Don Marcelino, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Don Marcelino Maruya Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Talagutong Elementary School in the Municipality of Don Marcelino, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Don Marcelino Maruya Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
